Package com.motorola.iden.crypto.spec

Class Summary
DHParameterSpec This class specifies the elliptic curves used to generate elliptic curve key-pairs.
ECKeyParameterSpec This class specifies the elliptic curves used to generate elliptic curve key-pairs and is not supported in the Gemini product.
IvParameterSpec This class specifies an initialization vector (IV).
RC5ParameterSpec This class specifies the parameters used with the RC5 algorithm.
